# Python Network Exposure & Security Analysis Tool

A final year cybersecurity project that scans authorised IP addresses for common TCP ports, identifies open services, explains potential exposure risks, calculates an exposure score, and saves results as a JSON report.

## Features
- IPv4 validation
- Common TCP port scanning
- Banner grabbing
- Risk analysis
- Exposure score
- JSON report generation

## Ethical Notice
Only scan systems you own or have permission to test.
